1
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:07,599
Miss Jiang,

2
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:11,640
I tricked you here with a little scheme.

3
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,280
You fools,

4
00:01:19,439 --> 00:01:21,239
you didn't even notice a stranger in your home.

5
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:23,680
Shutu.

6
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,319
Xunxun.

7
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:26,400
Shutu.

8
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:27,840
Shutu.

9
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,560
That woman just now,

10
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,799
she said she was Jiang Xun too.

11
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:32,159
Who is she?

12
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:33,959
She's just a delusional lunatic.

13
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:35,519
Don't worry about it.

14
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,120
I've already had someone teach her a lesson.

15
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:38,519
Okay.

16
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:41,239
Shutu,

17
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,359
do you remember

18
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:44,319
the piece of jade with plum blossom engraving

19
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:45,439
that I gave you before?

20
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:50,200
You mean the one

21
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,719
that you polished?

22
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,359
Yes, that's the one.

23
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,840
I recently got a new piece of jade.

24
00:01:58,359 --> 00:01:59,680
But I can't remember

25
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,200
the pattern of plum blossom.

26
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:03,719
Do you remember?

27
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:09,439
I can't remember it for the moment.

28
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,520
It doesn't matter.

29
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:16,439
We can think about it slowly.

30
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:17,439
Don't worry.

31
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,879
It's okay.

32
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,599
Jiang Xun.

33
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:12,479
I admit that I underestimated you before.

34
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,479
I didn't expect you to come to Harbor City alone.

35
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:17,919
I didn't expect

36
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:19,439
you to be willing to be my substitute

37
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,319
for Shen Shutu.

38
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:32,840
Except for Xue Li,

39
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,080
I'm the only one

40
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:36,919
who remembers what you want.

41
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,240
The patterns

42
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,960
are all in my mind.

43
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,560
If I die,

44
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,960
you'll get nothing.

45
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:52,759
Give me a piece of paper and a pen.

46
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,520
Test it.

47
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,720
That's it.

48
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:24,560
Go on.

49
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:27,079
Let Shen Shutu go,

50
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:29,879
and I'll tell you the rest patterns.

51
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:34,319
What if he doesn't want to leave?

52
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,720
After all,

53
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,000
I'm you now, Jiang Xun.

54
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:47,120
Whether I let Shen Shutu go or not,

55
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:49,560
you have to give me this thing.

56
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,680
until she confesses.

57
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:54,959
Yes.

58
00:04:55,959 --> 00:04:56,759
Let's go.

59
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:25,720
Mr. Feng,

60
00:05:26,079 --> 00:05:27,040
are you okay?

61
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,920
I'm fine.

62
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:29,959
Let's go.

63
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,680
Okay.

64
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,199
Mr. Feng,

65
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,319
thanks to your advance planning.

66
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,160
You've worked hard today.

67
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:46,240
Without your

68
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,680
suffering ruse,

69
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,519
Lin Chuyi wouldn't have believed

70
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,879
that he lost his memory.

71
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:51,920
From now on,

72
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,720
his actions should be smoother.

73
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,959
His acting is getting better.

74
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,360
From now on,

75
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,360
we're strangers.

76
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:26,319
I almost believed it.

77
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:29,920
To avoid alarming her,

78
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:32,560
[we need to lure her back to Rongzhou.]

79
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,199
[And as for Ke Yu'ang,]

80
00:06:33,839 --> 00:06:35,000
[we should try to use him to our advantage.]

81
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,360
Anyway,

82
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,279
thank you very much today.

83
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:40,920
It's my duty

84
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,279
to do this.

85
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,800
Alright, you should get some rest.

86
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,160
Call me if you need anything.

87
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:47,920
I'm leaving.

88
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:49,160
Take care.

89
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,160
What?

90
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,160
You let Jiang Xun get away?

91
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,560
There were many of them.

92
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,000
They knocked our people down.

93
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,040
Our base

94
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:00,519
has been exposed.

95
00:07:02,279 --> 00:07:03,800
You idiots.

96
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,800
Get out.

97
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,480
Xunxun,

98
00:07:16,759 --> 00:07:17,920
what happened?

99
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,079
Nothing.

100
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,360
Your wound hasn't healed yet.

101
00:07:27,399 --> 00:07:28,480
Why don't you go to bed?

102
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,600
Do you want me to stay with you?

103
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:32,800
I was

104
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:34,240
sitting here,

105
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:36,199
thinking about something.

106
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,879
What did you think about?

107
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,160
I remember

108
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,399
the old man told me

109
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,759
to come to Harbor City

110
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,600
to negotiate the cooperation as soon as possible

111
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,600
and then go back to the company.

112
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,279
You want to go back to Rongzhou.

113
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:52,720
No.

114
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,319
I just remembered.

115
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,560
And it's a bit embarrassing

116
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,480
to go back like this.

117
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:03,920
By the way,

118
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:05,519
didn't you ask me

119
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:07,279
about the pattern on that jade pendant?

120
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,720
I remember you drew it

121
00:08:09,759 --> 00:08:12,279
in your sketchbook at the studio.

122
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,879
In the studio's sketchbook?

123
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:16,279
Yeah.

124
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,560
It was on that table.

125
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,199
Manager Ke happened to come for you.

126
00:08:19,199 --> 00:08:19,839
Do you remember?

127
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:22,360
I remember now.

128
00:08:22,759 --> 00:08:23,959
Look at my memory.

129
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,160
It's getting late.

130
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:28,360
You should get some rest.

131
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,160
Okay.

132
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:31,480
You should get some rest too.

133
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,120
This is a manuscript from the Republic of China era

134
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,519
that I restored recently.

135
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:53,200
Great-Grandmother and Hideo had no affair.

136
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:56,159
And you and I are not what you think.

137
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,720
What are you talking about?

138
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,519
I borrowed this from the archive.

139
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,159
It's about Hideo

140
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:04,000
and your great-grandfather.

141
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,159
Hideo

142
00:09:14,519 --> 00:09:16,279
under the guise of saving patients,

143
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,559
he actually

144
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:20,000
conducted covert bacterial and viral experiments.

145
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,120
This is impossible.

146
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,159
My great-grandfather was a benevolent doctor.

147
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:36,039
The evidence is already in your hands.

148
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,480
Stop deceiving yourself.

149
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:40,000
He was not a benevolent doctor at all.

150
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,399
His hands are stained with blood.

151
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,399
He is a war criminal.

152
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:57,480
Senior fellow student,

153
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,919
you are not Yamazaki Hideo.

154
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,960
It's not too late to make amends.

155
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,960
As long as you cooperate with Rongzhou Security,

156
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:05,879
everything can start over.

157
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:15,919
You've done so much for her.

158
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:17,480
If you persist in your delusions,

159
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:19,519
the consequences are foreseeable.

160
00:10:27,679 --> 00:10:29,240
I asked you out here today

161
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,320
because I know

162
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:32,320
you've been helping me all along.

163
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,879
Without you,

164
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,480
I wouldn't have met Shen Shutu so soon.

165
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:39,000
I just worried about you,

166
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,279
and didn't want you to meet him.

167
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:44,159
Have you considered

168
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:46,559
what I said to you last time?

169
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,399
Senior,

170
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,240
you still

171
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,799
have a choice.

172
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:40,159
[Shen Shutu lost his memory after being injured,]

173
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,759
[and was completely unfamiliar with Jiang Xun who came to recognize him.]

174
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:45,200
[Jiang Xun tried to prove it with the token but failed.]

175
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,600
[Lin Chuyi's appearance]

176
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:48,240
[made the situation more complicated.]

177
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:51,639
[Lin Chuyi tested Shen Shutu with a piece of plum blossom-patterned cloth.]

178
00:11:51,759 --> 00:11:53,840
[His reaction was mysterious.]

179
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,200
[Jiang Xun was captured by Lin Chuyi's men]

180
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,919
[as soon as he left the villa.]

181
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:59,440
[A confrontation in the dark room is about to happen.]

182
00:11:59,759 --> 00:12:02,200
[Is Shen Shutu's amnesia due to the injury]

183
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,519
[or a well-planned trap?]

184
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:05,639
[Both sides are making preparations]

185
00:12:05,759 --> 00:12:06,759
[and waiting for the final showdown.]

186
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:09,039
[The final showdown is about to begin.]
